item.title: CVE-2020-5355|2024-09-16T16:52:53.903Z -- dell -- isilon%20onefs
item.description: The Dell Isilon OneFS versions 8.2.2 and earlier SSHD process improperly allows Transmission Control Protocol (TCP) and stream forwarding. This provides the remotesupport user and users with restricted shells more access than is intended.
